 <text id="F3060T">
  <front id="d2">
   <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
    <p>Demus writes that he does not like hearing that his wife is working in a field husking corn.
     He suggests that he might come home soon--as soon as he is paid the $90 owed to him.</p>
   </div1>
  </front>

  <body id="d4">
   <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
    <head>
     <name type="recipient">Mary Jane Demus</name>
    </head>

    <opener>
     <dateline>
      <date value="1863-11-08"><orig reg="november">nobember</orig> the 8th 1863</date>
     </dateline>
     <salute><orig reg="My">Mi</orig> Dear Wife</salute>
    </opener>

    <p>I <orig reg="take">tak</orig> this <orig reg="opportunity">optuity</orig> to <orig
      reg="inform">in form</orig> you that i am Well at present and <orig reg="hoping">hopein</orig>
     that <orig reg="these">thes</orig>
     <orig reg="few">fu</orig>
     <orig reg="lines">lynes</orig>
     <orig reg="may">ma</orig>
     <orig reg="find">finde</orig> you in the same state of <orig reg="health">healt</orig> i <orig
      reg="receive">recev</orig>
     <orig reg="your">yor</orig> letter on the 5th of this month and i Was <orig reg="very"
     >verry</orig> glad to hear <orig reg="from">frum</orig> you all and i <orig reg="happy"
     >hapey</orig> to hear that you have got such good <orig reg="health">healt</orig> since i left
      <orig reg="home">hom</orig> but i am <orig reg="afraid">a frad</orig> that you <orig reg="are"
      >ar</orig> going to <orig reg="hurt">heirt</orig>
     <orig reg="yourself">yor selfe</orig>
     <orig reg="Working">Warking</orig> i <orig reg="don't">doant</orig>
     <orig reg="think">thig</orig> that you <orig reg="ought">ot</orig> to go out in the <orig
      reg="field">feald</orig> to husk Corn or <orig reg="do">dow</orig>
     <orig reg="any">eney</orig> such <orig reg="Work">Wark</orig> i <orig reg="don't">doan</orig>
     <orig reg="think">thig</orig> nothing of you Working at Mr paterson <orig reg="some">som</orig>
     times but i <orig reg="don't">doant</orig> Want to hear of you going in the <orig reg="field"
      >feald</orig> to <orig reg="any">eney</orig> more and you <orig reg="need">nead</orig> mind
      <orig reg="What">Whot</orig> you <orig reg="hear">her</orig> all the <orig reg="talk"
     >tock</orig> that his son Can <orig reg="talk">tock</orig>
     <orig reg="Won't">Wont</orig>
     <orig reg="Hurt">Hirt</orig> you i he think that i <orig reg="Won't">Wont</orig> get home <orig
      reg="soon">son</orig> but i <orig reg="Would">Wod</orig> a <orig reg="Come">Cum</orig> home
     this time but i <orig reg="thought">thot</orig> We Will get <orig reg="our">ar</orig> money in
     a <orig reg="few">fu</orig> days and as <orig reg="soon">son</orig> as We get it i Will be at
     home to stay a Will and i have <orig reg="only">oney</orig> got a <orig reg="dollar"
     >doller</orig> now but if you <orig reg="look">lok</orig> in the <orig reg="next">nex</orig>
     letter i Will send you <orig reg="some">som</orig>
     <orig reg="home">hom</orig> We have got <orig reg="about">a bout</orig>
     <orig reg="ninety">nity</orig>
     <orig reg="Dollar">Dollre</orig>
     <orig reg="Coming">Cuming</orig> to us now and tell me how hold the thing <orig reg="for"
     >fer</orig> you you <unclear>sed</unclear>
     <unclear>robsen</unclear> boys <orig reg="What">Whot</orig>
     <unclear>robson</unclear> Was it <orig reg="for">fer</orig> i Want to now give <orig reg="my"
      >mi</orig> love to <orig reg="your">yor</orig> father and lysbeth and solomon harson and <orig
      reg="aunt">ant</orig> merrey harson and tell them to <orig reg="write">right</orig> to me
     Wants give <orig reg="my">mi</orig> love to all the <orig reg="friends">frends</orig></p>

    <p>nothing <orig reg="more">mor</orig> at Present but still <orig reg="remain">reman</orig></p>

    <closer>
     <salute><orig reg="your">yor</orig> Dear <orig reg="husband">husben</orig></salute>
     <signed>David Demus to <orig reg="mary">marrey</orig>
      <orig reg="Demus">Demes</orig></signed>
     <seg type="postscript"> Direct Mr David <orig reg="Demus">Demes</orig><lb/> Hilton Head SC<lb/>
      54th <abbr expan="Regiment">Regt</abbr><lb/>
      <orig reg="massachusetts">massahusets</orig><lb/>
      <orig reg="volunteers">volintears</orig>
     </seg>
    </closer>
   </div1>
  </body>
